OL,3,CTop Boy star Micheal Ward charged with
OL,4,Crape and sexual assault
OL,6,FTop Boy star Micheal Ward has been
OL,7,Fcharged with rape and sexual assault.
OL,9,FThe 27-year-old from Cheshunt,
OL,10,FHertfordshire, has been charged by the
OL,11,FMet Police with two counts of rape and
OL,12,Fthree counts of sexual assault.
OL,14,FThe offences relate to one woman and
OL,15,Fare reported to have taken place in
OL,16,FJanuary 2023.
OL,18,FWard has "entirely" denied the charges
OL,19,Fof rape and sexual assault and said he
OL,20,Fhas fully co-operated with police
OL,21,Fthroughout the investigation.
