OL,6,F"I recognise that proceedings are now
OL,7,Fongoing, and I have full faith that
OL,8,Fthey will lead to my name being
OL,9,Fcleared.
OL,11,F"Given those proceedings, I am unable
OL,12,Fto comment further."
OL,14,FDetective Superintendent Scott Ware,
OL,15,Fwhose team is leading the Met's
OL,16,Finvestigation, said: "Our specialist
OL,17,Fofficers continue to support the woman
OL,18,Fwho has come forward - we know
OL,19,Finvestigations of this nature can have
OL,20,Fsignificant impact on those who make
OL,21,Freports."
