OL,6,FWard will appear at Thames
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday, 28
OL,8,FAugust.
OL,10,FThe Jamaican-born actor was awarded
OL,11,Fthe Bafta Rising Star honour in 2020
OL,12,Fand was nominated for the Best
OL,13,FSupporting Actor Bafta for his role in
OL,14,FBBC's Small Axe in 2021 and the 2022
OL,15,Ffilm Empire Of Light.
