OL,6,FWard, who has 1.2 million followers on
OL,7,FInstagram, played in the Soccer Aid
OL,8,Fmatch at Stamford Bridge last year and
OL,9,Fgave a reading at the Christmas Eve
OL,10,Fcarol service hosted by the Princess
OL,11,Fof Wales in 2023.
OL,13,FHe is due to star in the American film
OL,14,FEddington alongside Joaquin Phoenix
OL,15,Fand Pedro Pascal, which is due to be
OL,16,Freleased in the UK next month.
